                    <span>This book is a short read, but one where the message is powerful! This book has creative, yet simple, descriptive names for places or people that are passed by through the journey that forces you to pause and reflect on your own path. I could not stop thinking about this parable for months after I read it, and would highly recommend it to others who want a positive tool to help reflect. I used this book as a professional development topic, where after reading this book, my staff explored their own professional paths to "destinae", while defining what that term meant for each of them. It was very well received!</span>
                  
